title: Aiseesoft Blu-ray Creator 1.0.16 + Patch [SWEG].rar
description:
Includes the Aiseesoft Blu-ray Creator v1.0.16 installation package, a patch and a text file containing instructions. The extra downloadable menu templates have also been included.

Install as usual. After installation use the provided patch. No serial number required. Done! Enjoy!


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Aiseesoft Blu-ray Creator allows you to create a Blu-ray disc, folder or ISO from any video. All video formats, including HD videos, are supported such as TS, M2TS, TP, TRP, MPG, MPEG, M4V, MP4, VOB, WMV, MXF etc. After burning, the Blu-ray disc can be played on various popular Blu-ray players such as PS3, Sony BDP-S5, Samsung BD-F, LG Electronics BP, etc.

You can add your favorite audio file as the background music. Insert subtitles in SRT, SSA and ASS formats. Themed menus with editable buttons, text, etc.

Aiseesoft Blu-ray Creator lets you trim and crop the video before converting as well. Video effects and a feature to add watermarks are also included in the software.
